Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Md
Web Item Name: Mechanix Wear Specialty 0.5mm Covert Tactical Gloves Covert Black M
Web Item Description:
Precision feel and high dexterity are synonymous with 0.5mm palm protection. Our Specialty 0.5mm Covert shooting gloves are built to deliver natural feel and lightweight hand protection in an anatomical design. 0.5mm AX-Suede provides the perfect blend of tactile control and protection in the field or at the shooting range. Breathable TrekDry conforms to the back of your hands to reduce heat build-up and expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility for smooth manipulation.

Features:

  • Low-profile Thermoplastic Rubber (TPR) closure provides a secure fit to the wrist.
  • Lightweight TrekDry conforms to the back of the hand to reduce heat build-up and perspiration.
  • Anatomical stitch darts conform to the natural curvature of the hand to create a precision fit.
  • Expandable flex joints improve trigger finger mobility.
  • High-dexterity 0.5mm AX-Suede™ provides precision feel and high dexterity.
  • Nylon carrier loops.
  • Machine washable.

Item Name: Alps Grand Slam (Standard)

The ALPS Grand Slam Turkey Vest is the ultimate turkey hunting vest on the market today.   • Five shell loops
  • Hydration compatible
  • Large game bag
  • Two side/water bottle pockets
  • Two mesh zippered pockets inside of vest
  • Side compression straps adjust to different body types

Item Name: Alps Impact Pro Vest
Web Item Name: Alps Outdoorz Impact Pro Turkey Hunting Vest Mossy Oak Original Bottomland
Web Item Description:
The Impact Pro has all the innovative features and essential conveniences of the original Impact with a series of bolstering upgrades that the serious turkey hunter will appreciate. The sit-anywhere design of the flip down seat now features a 1" molded and ergonomic foam design with dual-aluminum stays that is ideal for long sits. Both front panels feature molded pockets for added protection for your calls and gear. Each panel also includes a series of MOLLE webbing to allow you to customize your loadout with a number of different ALPS accessories. Speaking of accessories included with the Impact Pro is a redesigned box call pocket and an accessory ThermaCELL pocket both removable and both able to be mounted to either of the front panels.

Reinforced double and triple stitching ensures both comfort and durability when you need it most. Enjoy your hunt with this premium turkey vest and its XL game bag decoy stake pocket 8 gear pockets including one oversized rear storage pocket contoured shoulder strap design and many more features aimed to please the hardcore turkey enthusiast.

Item Name: Bloodline Dog Vest  Optifade Marsh L
Web Item Name: Rig'Em Right Bloodline Elite Dog Vest Optifade Marsh L
Web Item Description: The Bloodline Elite Dog Vest from Rig'Em Right Waterfowl offers the utmost protection for your most reliable hunting partner. The unique 3-layer construction of the upper material consists of 3mm neoprene gives a  next to "skin" for warmth and comfort. A thin layer of foam for added flotation and an outer layer of heavy-duty canvas for protection from brush and briers. Also features 5mm neoprene throughout the chest for flexibility and warmth and a sturdy braided handle to help you buddy back in the blind. This vest has a more athletic cut around the neck and between the front legs to provide better mobility without rubbing and bunching. Heavy duty zipper with velcro closure over zipper.
Manufacturer: AdvenTec LLC dba Rig Em Right Outdoors

Item Name: NUCLEUS HEATED BOTTOM BROWN CLAY 2XL
Web Item Name: Muddy Nucleus Heated Bottom Hunting Pants Brown Clay 2XL
Web Item Description: Perhaps the most important layer in any late-season whitetail hunter’s arsenal is a heated base layer that traps warmth and quickly generates more when your mind body and spirit need it most. Designed to serve as the core of your late-season layering system the Nucleus Heated Bottoms keep die-hard whitetail hunters warm through the worst conditions late season can dish out. Choose from low medium or high modes to activate the two heating elements on each thigh each powered by an included 10000mAh battery. The current setting can be altered using the silent push-button power control below the waistband. Easy to layer these bottoms are held in place when adding or removing additional articles of clothing thanks to integrated stirrup loops at the bottom of the pants. Pair their superb layer-ability with the anti-static and anti-pilling features of the fabric and you’ve got a key tree stand-hunting layering component that will withstand the longest coldest hunts for many seasons yet to come.

Item Name: NUCLEUS HEATED SOFTSHELL GLOVE BROWN CLAY LARGE
Web Item Name: Muddy Nucleus Heated Softshell Gloves Brown Clay L
Web Item Description: Nothing ruins a hunt quite as quickly as a couple of frozen fingers. This is exactly why you’ll want to keep our Nucleus Heated Softshell Gloves at the top of your must-have list from Muddy this fall. These heat-generating gloves boast three settings that keep your hands warm and fully functional and promote complete dexterity. While you wait for prime-time action to heat up choose the heat setting—low medium or high—best suited for the current conditions then let the integrated heating elements thoroughly warm your digits. When a shooting opportunity is presented flip open the top of your preferred shooting finger take the shot and then flip the magnetic closure back into place. And while cold weather equals regular deer movement throughout the day these hardworking hand warmers still account for the potential of a midday lull—helping you stay occupied thanks to tech tip index fingers that allow the use of mobile devices without ever removing them from your hands. Grip-resistant palm pads offer a rugged reinforced layer in areas where wear and tear occur most.

Web Item Name: Tenzing TR18 Turkey Recliner Hunting Vest Mossy Oak Bottomland

Item Name: MOJO Dove / Game Belt - SGB
Web Item Name: Mojo Outdoors Dove Game Belt Waist Pack Mossy Oak Shadow Grass Blades
Web Item Description:
Certain types of game hunting especially dove hunting requires the hunter to have ready access to many of the items used for the hunt plus a method of storing the harvested game off the ground. MOJO introduces the all-new Dove/Game Belt designed based on years of experience to provide those features needed during the hunt. Mojo dove hunting bag includes pockets and bags positioned around a sturdy 2-inch nylon belt with a convenient and adjustable snap buckle to fit most size hunters. Pockets include features such as:

  • Very convenient way to hunt dove or any other small game while on the move
  • Handy shell pouch with large opening for hand and zips up while not in use
  • Dove hunting bag has a handy cell phone pocket with magnetic closure for quick and easy access
  • Zippered accessory pouch with built in choke tube straps or holders
  • Large vented game bag with blood proof liner
  • Hunting game belt has handy drink pouch on side for favorite beverage
  • Double snap / push button buckle with heavy duty adjustable belt from approx. 28” to 56”
  • Separate zipper pouch built into game bag for MOJO poles wings and accessories

Made of High Strength Polyester Material with UV and Wear resistant features for long lasting durability.  BBased on our many years of experience this dove hunting belt bag will store and allow convenient access to the items needed for dove and other game hunting.

Item Name: Santiam Insulated Vest Gunmetal/Shadow Tan  M
Web Item Name: Santiam Insulated Vest Gunmetal/Shadow Tan  M

Item Name: Santiam Insulated Vest Gunmetal/Shadow Tan L
Web Item Name: Leupold Santiam Insulated Vest Gunmetal Shadow Tan L
Web Item Description:
When cool-weather conditions call for core warmth the Santiam Insulated Vest has you covered. It’s as stylish as it is functional and guaranteed to keep you warm without restricting your movement.

The Santiam Insulated Vest is durable water-resistant and offers the perfect balance between weight and warmth making it perfect for running early morning drills at the range setting up your treestand or hanging trail cameras in preparation for your next big hunt. The 20D ripstop DWR coated fabric protects you from the wind and keeps you dry in a light rain so you stay comfortable when conditions take a turn for the worse. Plus with 60 GMS of lightweight insulation this vest can be worn on its own or as an insulating layer for year-round warmth.

When temperatures drop keep warm and keep moving with the Santiam Insulated Vest whether you’re at the range in the field or out on the town.

Item Name: Moultrie Run N Gun 200-RT Edge Turkey Vest
Web Item Name: Knight & Hale Run N' Gun 200 Turkey Vest Realtree Edge
Web Item Description:
You'll know the instant you put on the Run N' Gun 200 that it isn't the typical hunting vest. First you can guarantee a good fit thanks to its 10-point adjustment system. With adjustments from the shoulders to your chest belly and lumber the Run N' Gun 200 is designed to stay in place without bagginess. This means you won't get constantly caught on limbs and any gear won't cause the vest to shift.

At just 1.5 lbs. the Run N' Gun 200 is one of the lightest on the market; you'll hardly know its there. The cinching system keeps the comfy removable six-layer cushioned seat against your butt for an easy sit-down or you can tuck it out of the way when it's not needed. Its built-in 198-cubic-inch backpack is also bladder compatible.

For gear storage the vest features four zippered pouches and five additional pockets for easy access to pot calls box calls strikers diaphragms your phone and any other accessory a turkey hunter could need. The incorporated MOLLE system allows for added pouches and more. You'll also get a decoy sling. Using a slip knot around the decoy's neck and a set loop around the tail the decoy sling can be quickly thrown over your head to keep decoy(s) secure againt your back while you chase birds.

This model comes in Realtree EDGE.

  • Better fit with less weight at just 1.5 lbs.
  • 10-point adjustment system for optimal fit
  • Hold-tight cinching seat system
  • Open construction allows for breathability keeping you cooler
  • Removable six-layer cushioned seat
  • 198-inch-cubic backpack with bladder compatibility
  • Numerous pockets slots and an integrated MOLLE system for carrying accessories
  • Weight: 1.5 lbs.
  • Camo pattern: Realtree EDGE
  • Integrated backpack: 198-cubic-inch
  • Multiple pockets for calls accessories and more
  • Removable seat cushion
  • Includes decoy sling
  • MOLLE system connections

Item Name: Moultrie Run N Gun 100-MO Bottonland Turkey Vest
Web Item Name: Knight & Hale Run N' Gun 100 Turkey Chest Rig Vest Mossy Oak Bottomland
Web Item Description:
The Run N' Gun 100 Turkey Chest Rig is designed for the mobile turkey hunter who relies on speed and stealth to get within range of a wary gobbler. It moves away from the traditional vest design where gear is located on the sides of the torso; instead the Chest Rig centrally locates all your essential gear right in front for fast and easy access. A rigid front hatch flips forward for easy viewing and call retrieval while strong magnetic snaps keep the hatch quietly and securely closed.

It features an internal striker holder and pot call pocket and there's plenty of room for your locator calls gloves face mask and more. Four external mesh pockets hold mouth calls and a large zippered pocket is great for licenses wallets or phones. There's also an integrated box call pouch with an elastic cinch cord.

With fully adjustable straps with quick-release buckles the Run N' Gun 100 Turkey Chest Rig securely holds your gear while still being easy to take on and off. This model comes in Mossy Oak Bottomland.

  • Ultra compact extremely lightweight design
  • Positions gear in front for easy retrieval
  • Adjustable universal fit
  • Multiple pockets and pouches for calls and other gear
  • Won't restrict airflow making it ideal for turkey hunting in warmer weather
  • Front-positioned turkey rig
  • Camo pattern: Mossy Oak Bottomland
  • Multiple pockets and pouches for gear
  • Quick-release buckles

Item Name: Run N' Gun 300-MO Bottomland Turkey Vest

Web Item Description:
Not a minimalist? Bring it all with the Run N’ Gun 300 Turkey Vest from Knight & Hale. This vest is the pinnacle for the hunter that likes to hunt efficiently prepared and coming in at just 2.5 lbs. you’ll hardly notice it as you trek the turkey woods.

The Run N’ Gun 300 offers an immense level of storage. Featuring nine zippered pockets a 375-cubic-inch backpack capable of holding a water bladder designated spaces for pot calls mouth calls a box call strikers 12/20/410 gauge shotgun shells a Thermacell a phone and a water bottle for good measure – the question isn’t “What should I leave behind?” it’s “Why should I leave anything behind?”

The semi-rigid back and six-layer cushioned seat offer tremendous support whether you’ve found your spot for the morning or need to find a nearby tree quickly – and with 10-points of adjustment you can be sure it will stay true to form from start to finish. Carry efficiently and hunt smarter with the Run N’ Gun 300 from Knight & Hale. 

This model comes in Mossy Oak Original Bottomland camo.

  • 10-point adjustment system for optimal fit
  • Hold-tight cinching seat system
  • Removable six-layer cushioned seat
  • 375-cubic-inch backpack with bladder compatibility and quick-access zipper
  • 9 zippered pockets on the front

  • ADJUSTABLE SECURE FIT: Customizable closure for maximum comfort and stability.
  • CONVENIENT CARRIER LOOPS: Integrated loops for effortless storage and accessibility on gear or belt.
  • MACHINE WASHABLE: Easily maintained cleanliness with up to 25 machine washes.
  • TRIED AND TESTED: Meets ANSI/ISEA 105 and EN 388 standards ensuring quality and safety.

Item Name: SHT EARLY SEASON 3/4 ZIP OVIX S
Web Item Name: Browning Early Season 3/4 Zip Shirt Ovix S
Web Item Description: The sun might be shining but warm weather hunting conditions bring challenges all their own. The Early Season 3/4 Zip Shirt is purpose-designed with long hot late summer/early fall days in mind. The lightweight polyester fabric is durable and features 50+ UPF sun protection to guard your skin against damaging solar rays. Human scent is always a concern so Silvadur technology has been added to provide long-lasting odor control. The 3/4 length zipper and strategically-placed mesh panels on the back and underarms maximize ventilation to keep you cool. Flatlock stitching reduces chafing. The tall collar helps keep the sun and backpack or sling straps off your neck.

Item Name: Browning SHT MONROE 1/4 ZIP OVIX M
Web Item Name: Browning Monroe 1/4 Zip Long Sleeve Shirt Ovix Camo M
Web Item Description:
Climate conditions are one of the biggest hurdles to overcome as a hunter. Whether it's the high country or hardwoods mornings can be cold and afternoons searing hot and humid. And variables like a breeze from the north or a blanket of clouds can keep the weather unpredictable all day long. Of course this just underscores the importance of proper layering and the need of the Monroe 1/4 Zip Shirt.

This 2 layer piece is constructed with a tough dura knit fleece outer and a warm fleece inner surface for the perfect combination of durability warmth and stretch-enhanced comfort. The addition of a DWR coating offers water resistance making the Monroe extra versatile as both an outer piece in warmer conditions and an ideal insulation layer under a parka.  

Features:

  • 2L dura knit fleece
  • Water-resistant DWR coating
  • SILVADUR technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • Front 1/4 zipper
  • Left chest zippered accessory pocket
  • Elastic bound cuffs with thumb loops
  • Ovix Camouflage

  • Adjustable button cuffs and longer sleeve plackets for easier roll-up
  • Regular Fit

Item Name: PNT WW FIELD PRO MOBL 36
Web Item Name:
Browning Field Pro Pant Mossy Oak Bottomland 36",

The Field Pro pant is versatile and comfortable making it a great addition to your hunting gear selection. Engineered with a 2L soft shell stretch fabric this pant is built for warmer weather waterfowl hunting with the right combination of durability wind and water resistance and just the right amount of stretch to optimize comfort. A DWR coating adds a level of water resistance. The soft inner lining adds comfort and warmth.

The Field Pro pant includes front and rear pockets plus a pair of cargo pockets on the thighs to keep your gear within easy reach. 13" long leg vents with zippered closures help keep you cool when the weather warms up or your activity level rises. Four-point knee articulation maximizes comfort and freedom of motion when getting into or out of your layout blind or walking along river banks. The comfortable cut allows for a base layer to be comfortably worn making the Field Pro pant an excellent outer layering piece for cooler drier weather.

Features:

  • Polyester stretch twill fabric with a soft backing
  • Highly wind resistant
  • Water-resistant DWR coating
  • SILVADUR technology provides long-lasting odor control
  • Deep zippered cargo pockets
  • Hand and rear pockets
  • 5 large belt loops
  • Side leg venting with 13" zippers
  • 4-point knee articulation for ease of movement
  • Size 32-40 with 32" inseam
  • Size 34-38 with 34" inseam

Engineered with a 2L soft shell stretch fabric this pant is built for warmer weather waterfowl hunting with the right combination of durability wind and water resistance and just the right amount of stretch to optimize comfort. A DWR coating adds a level of water resistance. The soft inner lining adds comfort and warmth.

The Field Pro pant includes front and rear pockets plus a pair of cargo pockets on the thighs to keep your gear within easy reach. 13" long leg vents with zippered closures help keep you cool when the weather warms up or your activity level rises. Four-point knee articulation maximizes comfort and freedom of motion when getting into or out of your layout blind or walking along river banks. The comfortable cut allows for a base layer to be comfortably worn making the Field Pro pant an excellent outer layering piece for cooler drier weather.

  • Hand and rear pockets

Item Name: Rugged Rare Elegant & Armed Concealed Carry Camisole (S)
Web Item Name: Cameleon Elegant & Armed Concealed Carry Camisole Black S
Web Item Description:
The Concealment Camisole was designed to be graceful and flowy yet structured enough to decrease “printing” or showing an outline of the gun through your clothes. Make it your own by dressing it up or down and pairing it with your favorite holster.

How to use:

Simply wear it overtop of your preferred holster and firearm for optimal concealment.

How it works:

Our patent-pending multi-layer design ensures the best possible concealment. The substantial underlayer is reinforced by eight panels – often called our 360-degree printing shields- that work to prevent an outline of the gun from showing through clothing.  The material on top creates dimension and movement further softening the appearance of any sharp edges. This innovative design creates a sleek look while providing you with the protection you need.

What holsters are compatible with the camisole?

Bellybands Kydex holsters the Enigma holster and even bra holsters.

Care Instructions:

Material- 100% Polyester
Lace- 90% Nylon 10% Spandex
Gentle cycle cold water air dry or tumble dry (low heat) steam or iron

Item Name: LIMBSAVER RECOIL PAD STRAP-ON BLACK 1-SIZE FITS ALL
Web Item Name: LimbSaver Strap-On Shooting Vest with Protective Shoulder Pad Black
Web Item Description:
The LimbSaver Shooting Vest is the ultimate solution for shooters who are looking for a way to reduce the intense kickback from their firearm. Whether you're an experienced shooter or just starting out this vest is designed to provide maximum comfort and protection.

With its protective shoulder pad made from LimbSaver's cutting-edge NAVCOM technology this shooting vest effectively reduces felt recoil making it ideal for extended shooting sessions or when using firearms without recoil pads. The NAVCOM material works by dissolving energy and vibration ensuring that your shoulder is protected from the toughest recoil.

Wearing the LimbSaver Shooting Vest is effortless simply slip it over your shoulder and clip it on. The vest is also compatible with LimbSaver recoil pads so you can experience the ultimate in recoil reduction.

So if you're looking for a way to reduce felt recoil and improve your shooting experience look no further than the LimbSaver Shooting Vest. Get yours today and start shooting with confidence!
